metadata.description:
Viviane presents the progress of the Monty team so far and the path they have taken.

00:00 Introduction to the Monty Project
00:57 Foundational Principles and Framework
05:11 Building the First Prototype
06:46 Advancements in Object Recognition
11:25 Implementing Evidence-Based Learning
14:41 Robustness and Generalization
21:18 Future Directions and Final Thoughts
